# Real Estate Landing Page - PHP Project

## 1. Project Overview
This project is a responsive Real Estate Landing Page developed using:
- PHP
- HTML
- CSS
- (Optional) MySQL for saving contact form leads

The landing page includes:
- Hero section with background banner and CTA button
- Property highlights (minimum 3 features using icons)
- Gallery section with at least 4 images
- Contact form with:
  - Name
  - Email
  - Phone
  - Property Type (dropdown)
  - Checkbox (“I want a site visit”)
- Form validation on submission
- Success or error message displayed on the same page
- (Optional) Saving leads to a MySQL database
- (Optional) A separate page (submitted-leads.php) to list saved leads

------------------------------------------------------------

## 2. Folder Structure

project/
│── index.php  
│── css/style.css  
│── images/ (contains all gallery and banner images)  
│── leads.php (optional – used only if form data is saved in DB)  
│── submitted-leads.php (optional – list of saved leads)  
│── database.sql (optional – export of MySQL database)

